      "seed": 446359414,
      "version": 430,
      "versionNonce": 526992713,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "核心线程数(corePoolSize)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "uz0TVmco2R59B-Yi8uWkC",
      "originalText": "核心线程数(corePoolSize)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "s7kZEgNF9emN4mUgIwt6o",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2254.2413896379567,
      "y": 9047.08394719041,
      "width": 660,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fhC2E2d0PoYY0t6UhYPAq",
        "llsW3dZ67JK_ARZJQO0R3"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9yv",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 511832810,
      "version": 406,
      "versionNonce": 1521438663,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "核心线程数的设计需要依据任务的处理时间和每秒产生的任务数量来确定。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "核心线程数的设计需要依据任务的处理时间和每秒产生的任务数量来确定。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "OYqXXTHE2fGcoXlCrkTp2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2254.2413896379567,
      "y": 9077.38692365127,
      "width": 787.3199462890625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fhC2E2d0PoYY0t6UhYPAq",
        "llsW3dZ67JK_ARZJQO0R3"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9yw",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2029684918,
      "version": 387,
      "versionNonce": 1719907369,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "例如：一个线程执行一个任务需要0.1秒，1秒就执行10个任务；系统80%的时间每秒都会\n产生100个任务，那么要想在1秒内处理完这100个任务，就需要10个线程。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "例如：一个线程执行一个任务需要0.1秒，1秒就执行10个任务；系统80%的时间每秒都会产生100个任务，那么要想在1秒内处理完这100个任务，就需要10个线程。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Hk1Dk27m0-Lwz0Nd0rGGB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2254.2413896379567,
      "y": 9132.68990011213,
      "width": 328.65997314453125,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fhC2E2d0PoYY0t6UhYPAq",
        "llsW3dZ67JK_ARZJQO0R3"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9yx",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 274204074,
      "version": 387,
      "versionNonce": 2078260967,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "此时我们就可以设计核心线程数为10;",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "此时我们就可以设计核心线程数为10;",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "NWJbxlm0FpmEd-H-OzHYE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2254.2413896379567,
      "y": 9162.99287657299,
      "width": 782.6599731445312,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fhC2E2d0PoYY0t6UhYPAq",
        "llsW3dZ67JK_ARZJQO0R3"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9yy",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1163133430,
      "version": 380,
      "versionNonce": 36521737,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "当然实际情况不可能这么平均，所以我们一般按照二八原则设计即可，即按照80%的情况\n设计核心线程数，剩下的20%可以利用最大线程数处理;",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "当然实际情况不可能这么平均，所以我们一般按照二八原则设计即可，即按照80%的情况设计核心线程数，剩下的20%可以利用最大线程数处理;",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "2tfQ02LStLNzTSvWETB0a",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -2254.2413896379567,
      "y": 9218.29585303385,
      "width": 248,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#eebefa",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fhC2E2d0PoYY0t6UhYPAq",
        "llsW3dZ67JK_ARZJQO0R3"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
