    {
      "id": "O30OMXx_Q5AN_en02s5iz",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2248.9413102922535,
      "y": 9389.50775887729,
      "width": 279.39984130859375,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fhC2E2d0PoYY0t6UhYPAq",
        "llsW3dZ67JK_ARZJQO0R3"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9z4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1162706358,
      "version": 351,
      "versionNonce": 505927593,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "最大线程数(maximumPoolSize)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "gf7QwtfqEjr4okwBkCK9u",
      "originalText": "最大线程数(maximumPoolSize)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "CsaVfFjxEHqfKv50BCeij",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2254.2413896379567,
      "y": 9424.81073533815,
      "width": 886.478564939358,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fhC2E2d0PoYY0t6UhYPAq",
        "llsW3dZ67JK_ARZJQO0R3"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9z5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 513466538,
      "version": 441,
      "versionNonce": 446796647,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "最大线程数的设计除了需要参照核心线程数的条件外，还需要参照系统每秒产生的最大任务数决定；",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "最大线程数的设计除了需要参照核心线程数的条件外，还需要参照系统每秒产生的最大任务数决定；",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "TDK6cRDZEDR7oCzgME8kG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2254.2413896379567,
      "y": 9455.11371179901,
      "width": 608,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fhC2E2d0PoYY0t6UhYPAq",
        "llsW3dZ67JK_ARZJQO0R3"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9z6",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1434474230,
      "version": 362,
      "versionNonce": 142670473,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "例如：上述环境中，如果系统每秒最大产生的任务是1000个，那么：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "例如：上述环境中，如果系统每秒最大产生的任务是1000个，那么：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "e_7zH3QORWbkigZ1AFS1Q",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -2254.2413896379567,
      "y": 9485.41668825987,
      "width": 595,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffd8a8",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fhC2E2d0PoYY0t6UhYPAq",
        "llsW3dZ67JK_ARZJQO0R3"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9z7",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1764884842,
      "version": 272,
      "versionNonce": 2013826695,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "a87rxPuBeX7aDYZ-WM1oP",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "a87rxPuBeX7aDYZ-WM1oP",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2248.9213212785817,
      "y": 9490.41668825987,
      "width": 584.35986328125,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fhC2E2d0PoYY0t6UhYPAq",
        "llsW3dZ67JK_ARZJQO0R3"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9z8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 42810218,
      "version": 380,
      "versionNonce": 1433583977,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "最大线程数 = ( 最大任务数 - 任务队列长度 ) * 单个任务执行时间；",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "e_7zH3QORWbkigZ1AFS1Q",
      "originalText": "最大线程数 = ( 最大任务数 - 任务队列长度 ) * 单个任务执行时间；",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "xJ8PjKfv1807F6gD_H4tb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2254.2413896379567,
      "y": 9525.71966472073,
      "width": 423.45977783203125,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fhC2E2d0PoYY0t6UhYPAq",
        "llsW3dZ67JK_ARZJQO0R3"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9z9",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 612763702,
      "version": 364,
      "versionNonce": 19080615,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "即： 最大线程数 = (1000 - 200 ) * 0.1 = 80个；",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "即： 最大线程数 = (1000 - 200 ) * 0.1 = 80个；",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MzPs5yiNbeJmlXW7zJttx",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -2254.2413896379567,
      "y": 9556.02264118159,
      "width": 278,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#eebefa",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fhC2E2d0PoYY0t6UhYPAq",
        "llsW3dZ67JK_ARZJQO0R3"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9zA",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1204716778,
