      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "最大空闲时间(keepAliveTime)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "MzPs5yiNbeJmlXW7zJttx",
      "originalText": "最大空闲时间(keepAliveTime)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "oFbj1wlaue4a_ATvHlqp8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2254.2413896379567,
      "y": 9596.32561764245,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fhC2E2d0PoYY0t6UhYPAq",
        "llsW3dZ67JK_ARZJQO0R3"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9zC",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 37982582,
      "version": 370,
      "versionNonce": 383662889,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这个参数的设计完全参考系统运行环境和硬件压力设定，没有固定的参考值，用户可以根据\n经验和系统产生任务的时间间隔合理设置一个值即可。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "这个参数的设计完全参考系统运行环境和硬件压力设定，没有固定的参考值，用户可以根据经验和系统产生任务的时间间隔合理设置一个值即可。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "UiAOIDyoS7iwM7Z_JBzK7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2254.2413896379567,
      "y": 9295.16701060756,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
