      "versionNonce": 1245468551,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "实际上submit中最终还是调用的execute()方法，只不过会返回一个Future对象，用来获取任务执行结果：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "实际上submit中最终还是调用的execute()方法，只不过会返回一个Future对象，用来获取任务执行结果：",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "A80IIYe5w87_nOr89sehv",
