      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "execute(Runnable command)方法执行时会分为三步：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "execute(Runnable command)方法执行时会分为三步：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Wki5l_yUVdX-U8qAoSmu5",
      "type": "image",
      "x": -4426.8085995417705,
      "y": 10757.67395386147,
      "width": 824.7154471544716,
      "height": 634,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "transparent",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "rSR5Dr4n3yzI9S6XOi09x",
        "Ld3G-fgFq1R-X2icvYPrq"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9zQ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 408114666,
      "version": 581,
      "versionNonce": 1913721673,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "status": "saved",
      "fileId": "b0ba177e51ad101da0cdd56d4e3a47ca4af31f33",
      "scale": [
        1,
        1
      ],
      "crop": null
    },
    {
      "id": "2473_q4xMoAg1MRVEF7Ty",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4426.8085995417705,
      "y": 11407.4605935741,
      "width": 975.4049321769388,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "rSR5Dr4n3yzI9S6XOi09x",
        "Ld3G-fgFq1R-X2icvYPrq"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9zR",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 592875382,
      "version": 658,
      "versionNonce": 1102275015,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "注意：提交一个Runnable时，不管当前线程池中的线程是否空闲，只要数量小于核心线程数就会创建新线程。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "注意：提交一个Runnable时，不管当前线程池中的线程是否空闲，只要数量小于核心线程数就会创建新线程。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QBIOpMeLzPrft1JlKN7go",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4426.8085995417705,
      "y": 11438.63440526098,
      "width": 1091.0700112443565,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "rSR5Dr4n3yzI9S6XOi09x",
        "Ld3G-fgFq1R-X2icvYPrq"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9zS",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1320471274,
      "version": 698,
      "versionNonce": 1862386217,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "注意：ThreadPoolExecutor相当于是非公平的，比如队列满了之后提交的Runnable可能会比正在排队的Runnable先执行。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "注意：ThreadPoolExecutor相当于是非公平的，比如队列满了之后提交的Runnable可能会比正在排队的Runnable先执行。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "6Z7W8JvYOrV9PRbA1EYfM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4904.364283240536,
      "y": 6939.128496836113,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "a5tZpARgDyId3BHbKC4mT",
        "LmnUfBvO5wJu-1Cu_vPM7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9zT",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1455494634,
      "version": 411,
      "versionNonce": 1284608231,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "线程池有如下的优势：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "线程池有如下的优势：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rPcumqyeNkrC55aNTz9q7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4904.364283240536,
      "y": 6967.438950580915,
      "width": 793.760009765625,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "a5tZpARgDyId3BHbKC4mT",
        "LmnUfBvO5wJu-1Cu_vPM7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9zU",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1106449846,
      "version": 407,
      "versionNonce": 733582601,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 降低资源消耗：通过池化技术重复利用已创建的线程，降低线程创建和销毁造成的损耗。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 降低资源消耗：通过池化技术重复利用已创建的线程，降低线程创建和销毁造成的损耗。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "sbvUGodwftUoQoBQflSSE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4904.364283240536,
      "y": 6995.749404325718,
      "width": 573.760009765625,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "a5tZpARgDyId3BHbKC4mT",
        "LmnUfBvO5wJu-1Cu_vPM7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9zV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1522190506,
      "version": 407,
      "versionNonce": 907860999,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 提高响应速度：任务到达时，无需等待线程创建即可立即执行。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 提高响应速度：任务到达时，无需等待线程创建即可立即执行。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "DM-d69Zb-oPM9nEXwq_r4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4904.364283240536,
      "y": 7024.05985807052,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "a5tZpARgDyId3BHbKC4mT",
        "LmnUfBvO5wJu-1Cu_vPM7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9zW",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1504898806,
      "version": 438,
      "versionNonce": 1806961641,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 提高线程的可管理性：线程是稀缺资源，如果无限制创建，不仅会消耗系统资源，还会因\n为线程的不合理分布导致资源调度失衡，降低系统的稳定性。使用线程池可以进行统一的分\n配、调优和监控。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 提高线程的可管理性：线程是稀缺资源，如果无限制创建，不仅会消耗系统资源，还会因为线程的不合理分布导致资源调度失衡，降低系统的稳定性。使用线程池可以进行统一的分配、调优和监控。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "fZ51_hUI341YThowO5KpX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4904.364283240536,
      "y": 7102.3703118153235,
      "width": 796.219970703125,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "a5tZpARgDyId3BHbKC4mT",
        "LmnUfBvO5wJu-1Cu_vPM7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9zX",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 40903530,
      "version": 461,
      "versionNonce": 1649525543,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 提供更多更强大的功能：线程池具备可拓展性，允许开发人员向其中增加更多的功能。比\n如延时定时线程池ScheduledThreadPoolExecutor，就允许任务延期执行或定期执行。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 提供更多更强大的功能：线程池具备可拓展性，允许开发人员向其中增加更多的功能。比如延时定时线程池ScheduledThreadPoolExecutor，就允许任务延期执行或定期执行。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "F60is3C4RqF0bleZQVYUg",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4900.955339535832,
      "y": 6751.19626770963,
      "width": 100,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "QAOhDtwcf6eJmS8BL6UgZ",
        "LmnUfBvO5wJu-1Cu_vPM7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9zY",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 56093494,
      "version": 351,
      "versionNonce": 1996269257,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "线程池简介",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "线程池简介",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Ehob6hAE_Jku0fmsTOTGs",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4900.955339535832,
      "y": 6784.43832215323,
      "width": 923.1217672000828,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "QAOhDtwcf6eJmS8BL6UgZ",
        "LmnUfBvO5wJu-1Cu_vPM7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9zZ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1859652394,
      "version": 541,
      "versionNonce": 27051591,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "线程池（Thread Pool）是一种基于池化思想管理线程的工具，经常出现在多线程服务器中，如Tomcat。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "线程池（Thread Pool）是一种基于池化思想管理线程的工具，经常出现在多线程服务器中，如Tomcat。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "O6_g_m16Qwu_Vw1bF2Ncn",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4900.955339535832,
      "y": 6850.92243104043,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "QAOhDtwcf6eJmS8BL6UgZ",
        "LmnUfBvO5wJu-1Cu_vPM7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9za",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 316740726,
      "version": 455,
      "versionNonce": 137291177,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "线程池维护多个线程，等待监督管理者分配可并发执行的任务。\n一方面避免了处理任务时创建销毁线程开销的代价；\n另一方面避免了线程数量膨胀导致的过分调度问题，保证了对内核的充分利用。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "线程池维护多个线程，等待监督管理者分配可并发执行的任务。\n一方面避免了处理任务时创建销毁线程开销的代价；\n另一方面避免了线程数量膨胀导致的过分调度问题，保证了对内核的充分利用。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "3G8IXrVutmlWsxBi5gRZv",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4900.955339535832,
      "y": 6817.68037659683,
      "width": 1000,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "QAOhDtwcf6eJmS8BL6UgZ",
        "LmnUfBvO5wJu-1Cu_vPM7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9zb",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1772319978,
      "version": 405,
      "versionNonce": 47867239,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "线程过多会带来额外的开销，其中包括创建销毁线程的开销、调度线程的开销等，同时也降低了计算机的整体性能",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "线程过多会带来额外的开销，其中包括创建销毁线程的开销、调度线程的开销等，同时也降低了计算机的整体性能",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
