      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "状态转换",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "xBkPihuoRGgI2irY4V-At",
      "originalText": "状态转换",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "kTySySJIDQxU_m_rRd1-B",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3154.083620939986,
      "y": 10698.619608091522,
      "width": 1051.6920983382165,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "OA9DiJ8NlfF0M8d5NbYbt",
        "PZVIgb7rBf2__cG0I88gU",
        "9D6_ud6-Dp770gIo6nlwP"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA2M",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 577776694,
      "version": 287,
      "versionNonce": 956143849,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1.RUNNING -> SHUTDOWN：手动调用shutdown()触发，或者线程池对象GC时会调用finalize()从而调用shutdown()",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1.RUNNING -> SHUTDOWN：手动调用shutdown()触发，或者线程池对象GC时会调用finalize()从而调用shutdown()",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "HC6wLZkpf4MPf_4KuJYfT",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3154.083620939986,
      "y": 10730.040660663646,
      "width": 1334.5201768176248,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "OA9DiJ8NlfF0M8d5NbYbt",
        "PZVIgb7rBf2__cG0I88gU",
        "9D6_ud6-Dp770gIo6nlwP"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA2N",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 488659498,
      "version": 362,
      "versionNonce": 301172263,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2.(RUNNING or SHUTDOWN) -> STOP：调用shutdownNow()触发，如果先调shutdown()紧着调shutdownNow()，就会发生SHUTDOWN -> STOP",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2.(RUNNING or SHUTDOWN) -> STOP：调用shutdownNow()触发，如果先调shutdown()紧着调shutdownNow()，就会发生SHUTDOWN -> STOP",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "aLQjLx6W7FfhNvX4Wnzla",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3154.083620939986,
      "y": 10761.46171323577,
      "width": 647.6798095703125,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "OA9DiJ8NlfF0M8d5NbYbt",
        "PZVIgb7rBf2__cG0I88gU",
        "9D6_ud6-Dp770gIo6nlwP"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA2O",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 122238326,
      "version": 231,
      "versionNonce": 1569493961,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3.SHUTDOWN -> TIDYING：队列为空并且线程池中没有线程时自动转换",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3.SHUTDOWN -> TIDYING：队列为空并且线程池中没有线程时自动转换",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "qvGLqZaUV-wAxBc33XmPd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3154.083620939986,
      "y": 10792.882765807895,
      "width": 677.83984375,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "OA9DiJ8NlfF0M8d5NbYbt",
        "PZVIgb7rBf2__cG0I88gU",
        "9D6_ud6-Dp770gIo6nlwP"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA2P",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1428653290,
      "version": 243,
      "versionNonce": 2114857287,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "4.STOP -> TIDYING：线程池中没有线程时自动转换（队列中可能还有任务）",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4.STOP -> TIDYING：线程池中没有线程时自动转换（队列中可能还有任务）",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p-TUAld4ZimVK1Or-4PRI",
