      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 592654710,
      "version": 279,
      "versionNonce": 1361665129,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "我们一般会使用thread.start()方法来开启一个线程，那如何停掉一个线程呢？",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "我们一般会使用thread.start()方法来开启一个线程，那如何停掉一个线程呢？",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Wx3iDNyoq-3FhElz4IPEg",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4335.140668114173,
      "y": 11692.691664947562,
      "width": 747.139892578125,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "HgucmRJ6JyPnBFR-k2b7S",
        "VtFNiggRveHe4cO45rjst"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA2V",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1405831402,
      "version": 299,
      "versionNonce": 905427623,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "线程池中就是利用线程中断机制来停止线程的。比如shutdownNow()方法中会调用：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "线程池中就是利用线程中断机制来停止线程的。比如shutdownNow()方法中会调用：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "C7SHtNQeTuYFrvXhmCoVR",
      "type": "image",
