      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "线程发生异常，会被移出线程池吗？",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "7F7jbKlDMzxauAqgoLDFa",
      "originalText": "线程发生异常，会被移出线程池吗？",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "OWV-L1ja2O9G_7haISKBS",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3406.129857269895,
      "y": 11668.714573893021,
      "width": 902.1525160280776,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "k_zlcIlu_OQmXR9dSCoZf",
        "VtFNiggRveHe4cO45rjst"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA2a",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1440893238,
      "version": 479,
      "versionNonce": 1215785225,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "答案是会的，那有没有可能核心线程数在执行任务时都出错了，导致所有核心线程都被移出了线程池？",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "答案是会的，那有没有可能核心线程数在执行任务时都出错了，导致所有核心线程都被移出了线程池？",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "4aIZUUAkpEXYTC7OEmIEs",
      "type": "image",
      "x": -3406.129857269895,
      "y": 11761.465086106631,
      "width": 964.0549102428722,
      "height": 634,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "transparent",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "k_zlcIlu_OQmXR9dSCoZf",
        "VtFNiggRveHe4cO45rjst"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA2b",
