      "versionNonce": 1357591111,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "线程池为什么一定得是阻塞队列？",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "54xF_4ttTJzP0YQ25_EwU",
      "originalText": "线程池为什么一定得是阻塞队列？",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "AFvYZwYV4Mms5-AT_siVE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4341.17193763905,
      "y": 12059.259581197091,
      "width": 884.7401553414738,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Rkuv_Iu0pVAGdpqUbh84C",
        "VtFNiggRveHe4cO45rjst"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA2g",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 469095286,
      "version": 373,
      "versionNonce": 1817000361,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "线程池中的线程在运行过程中，执行完创建线程时绑定的第一个任务后，就会不断的从队列中获取任\n务并执行，那么如果队列中没有任务了，线程为了不自然消亡，就会阻塞在获取队列任务时，等着队\n列中有任务过来就会拿到任务从而去执行任务。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "线程池中的线程在运行过程中，执行完创建线程时绑定的第一个任务后，就会不断的从队列中获取任务并执行，那么如果队列中没有任务了，线程为了不自然消亡，就会阻塞在获取队列任务时，等着队列中有任务过来就会拿到任务从而去执行任务。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "x8Y_HsLS7ij5dG7snWMBi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4339.479131149579,
      "y": 12142.735906771091,
      "width": 720,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Rkuv_Iu0pVAGdpqUbh84C",
        "VtFNiggRveHe4cO45rjst"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA2h",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 630965994,
      "version": 351,
      "versionNonce": 897274215,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "通过这种方法能最终确保，线程池中能保留指定个数的核心线程数，关键代码为：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "通过这种方法能最终确保，线程池中能保留指定个数的核心线程数，关键代码为：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vpVZLrZg9m59p0QTliu9r",
      "type": "image",
      "x": -4342.1110460333175,
      "y": 12174.00189799294,
      "width": 495,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "transparent",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Rkuv_Iu0pVAGdpqUbh84C",
        "VtFNiggRveHe4cO45rjst"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA2i",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1755135478,
      "version": 329,
      "versionNonce": 1873419401,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "status": "saved",
      "fileId": "14968c3d4762016e041760b0ea58c32aca2f2469",
      "scale": [
        1,
        1
      ],
      "crop": null
    },
    {
      "id": "cg5T3KejApIiG0LPOd8xp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4320.332761684824,
      "y": 12453.411185397881,
      "width": 854.5587301513599,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Rkuv_Iu0pVAGdpqUbh84C",
        "VtFNiggRveHe4cO45rjst"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA2j",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1308282922,
      "version": 382,
      "versionNonce": 1291488391,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "某个线程在从队列获取任务时，会判断是否使用超时阻塞获取，\n我们可以认为非核心线程会poll()，非核心线程超过时间还没获取到任务后面就会自然消亡了。\n核心线程会take()，",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "某个线程在从队列获取任务时，会判断是否使用超时阻塞获取，\n我们可以认为非核心线程会poll()，非核心线程超过时间还没获取到任务后面就会自然消亡了。\n核心线程会take()，",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
