      "versionNonce": 662616263,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775193057423,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "失败两个原因，\na.线程池非RUNNING；\nb.核心线程满",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "5r__04Doi8tSN1uSRqKzc",
      "originalText": "失败两个原因，\na.线程池非RUNNING；\nb.核心线程满",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "nXWpNgTQiREqpPaIp6mFp",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -3884.380044599659,
      "y": 13855.720750190414,
      "width": 190.08152999068534,
      "height": 23.661601243653422,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "2MOq2q-DuAOkg3sDSttD9",
        "i3MItnWpZAbFjQBBMHYcX",
        "4c4qpDqE6AAzkUKZPv_5R",
        "txwuPr08YYPjUOQdbvwiL",
        "S9vw2tNzqfiJRg0p2GgAp"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA55z",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1998102720,
      "version": 312,
      "versionNonce": 528177961,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "0zlUCWyve9LHYAqfumBhA",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1775193057423,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "jzxORUoFc_IaIxLru0jnE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1298.0673205729959,
      "y": 16915.283972980924,
      "width": 426.2957238149111,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "S9vw2tNzqfiJRg0p2GgAp"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA56",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1398087872,
      "version": 214,
      "versionNonce": 1666173897,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "如果前面的条件判断都不满足（即线程池状态未\n达到 STOP，不是突然终止，且当前工作线程数\n量小于 min），则调用 addWorker 方法添加一\n个新的非核心线程来处理工作队列中的任务",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "如果前面的条件判断都不满足（即线程池状态未达到 STOP，不是突然终止，且当前工作线程数量小于 min），则调用 addWorker 方法添加一个新的非核心线程来处理工作队列中的任务",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "NpO7YNZdhBO4uVv86kZCh",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -635.8342429176678,
      "y": 14857.380927376531,
      "width": 783.7998657226562,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA57",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1128428352,
      "version": 210,
      "versionNonce": 322597191,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "如果满足条件则 timed 为 true，后续会使用非阻塞或带超时的方式从队列获取任务；否则\n使用阻塞方式获取任务。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "如果满足条件则 timed 为 true，后续会使用非阻塞或带超时的方式从队列获取任务；否则使用阻塞方式获取任务。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "cNjy2HlWZYpB9SuDV45aB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -453.41104758017264,
      "y": 15125.068837847166,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA58",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 473047872,
      "version": 77,
      "versionNonce": 685075113,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775143332472,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "判断工作线程数是否超过最大线程数，或者（允许超时且上次轮询超时），并且（工作线程\n数大于1或者工作队列为空），如果满足条件则尝试通过\ncompareAndDecrementWorkerCount(c) 以原子方式减少工作线程数，如果成功则返回\nnull，表示当前工作线程可以结束",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "判断工作线程数是否超过最大线程数，或者（允许超时且上次轮询超时），并且（工作线程数大于1或者工作队列为空），如果满足条件则尝试通过 compareAndDecrementWorkerCount(c) 以原子方式减少工作线程数，如果成功则返回 null，表示当前工作线程可以结束",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
