      "seed": 1160468617,
      "version": 319,
      "versionNonce": 782460905,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1775184678765,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "XAROLLBACK+XACOMMIT指令（Netty协议（基于TCP））\n1、TC发送指令通过TCP协议，若TCP中断，TC再次重试\n2、执行失败会告诉TC，TC再次重试\n3、执行成功不会告诉TC，所以TC只有收到失败会重试\n失败均无限重试",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "XAROLLBACK+XACOMMIT指令（Netty协议（基于TCP））\n1、TC发送指令通过TCP协议，若TCP中断，TC再次重试\n2、执行失败会告诉TC，TC再次重试\n3、执行成功不会告诉TC，所以TC只有收到失败会重试\n失败均无限重试",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
