      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1775150771995,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "7.若任一Try失败则调用RM-A和RM-B的cancel方法\n若Try均成功则调用RM-A和RM-B的confirm方法",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "8kgTtXpKe30jX9IKQToka",
      "originalText": "7.若任一Try失败则调用RM-A和RM-B的cancel方法\n若Try均成功则调用RM-A和RM-B的confirm方法",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "RpvfKbxVLQ8fayCDUadM-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1966.651411841994,
      "y": -193.45505956962813,
      "width": 481.52001953125,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "hA4W2An8lD1XL5oEgz16o"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA7t",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1956945193,
      "version": 532,
      "versionNonce": 1119071881,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775149762353,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "confirm和cancel方法(Netty协议（基于TCP）)\n1、TC调用方法，若TCP中断，TC再次重试\n2、执行失败会告诉TC，TC再次重试\n3、执行成功不会告诉TC，所以TC只有收到失败会重试\n失败均无限重试",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "confirm和cancel方法(Netty协议（基于TCP）)\n1、TC调用方法，若TCP中断，TC再次重试\n2、执行失败会告诉TC，TC再次重试\n3、执行成功不会告诉TC，所以TC只有收到失败会重试\n失败均无限重试",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
