    {
      "id": "uftqPPcY8ZHwsoRFz_Nxf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 408.24327931986454,
      "y": 1982.2035241010503,
      "width": 538.9197998046875,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cA8t",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1163457095,
      "version": 358,
      "versionNonce": 2034409833,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775186765571,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "XAROLLBACK+XACOMMIT指令（Netty协议（基于TCP））\n1、TC发送指令通过TCP协议，若TCP中断，TC再次重试\n2、执行失败会告诉TC，TC再次重试\n3、执行成功不会告诉TC，所以TC只有收到失败会重试\n失败均无限重试",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "XAROLLBACK+XACOMMIT指令（Netty协议（基于TCP））\n1、TC发送指令通过TCP协议，若TCP中断，TC再次重试\n2、执行失败会告诉TC，TC再次重试\n3、执行成功不会告诉TC，所以TC只有收到失败会重试\n失败均无限重试",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
